<br>
Now, soloing is where I need help...  I am having severe trouble understanding the concept of quad kiting, and I always seem to die, or get horrible xp while single kiting/root-nuking a monster by myself.  If someone could help me out with this, I would be quite glad.  Thanks.<br>
<br>
-Eledaar Darkpyre, 38 Wizard<br>
Dragons of Kel'Dar<br>
Xegony <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/unucle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nucle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/29/01 1:28:52 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Would someone mind helping me out wtih some info?</span><hr size=1> There is a lot of information on this subject already posted on the board here...<br>
